videos.description: Marquez Callaway jumps and uses every inch of his body to make a one-handed touchdown catch to put the Volunteers in the lead.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Callaway makes impressive one-handed TD catch

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur connects with C.J. Duncan who drags a defender into the end zone with him for a 9-yard Commodores touchdown.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Duncan muscles his way into the end zone

videos.description: John Kelly shows off his athleticism by jumping over the pile for a touchdown to put the Volunteers back on top.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Kelly soars for TD

videos.description: Ralph Webb almost sticks the landing when he flips his way into the end zone for a 2-yard Commodores touchdown.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Webb flips into the end zone

videos.description: The Commodores confuse the Volunteers' defense with a flea flicker and Kyle Shurmur passes it to a wide open Kalija Lipscomb for an easy touchdown.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt uses flea flicker for TD

videos.description: Vanderbilt head coach Derek Mason lays out how his quarterback Kyle Shurmur has to keep leading his team going into the second half and how the defense needs to keep rolling.
videos.headline: Mason: 'We have to adapt and adjust'

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur connects with an open Trent Sherfield in the end zone for a 20-yard touchdown to pad the Commodores' lead.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Shurmur finds Sherfield for TD

videos.description: Ralph Webb finds a gap in the defense and bursts for a 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Webb rushes forTD

videos.description: Senior running back Ralph Webb gets emotional talking about his last career start and all he has been through this season.
videos.headline: Webb: 'I just kept pushing through'
